overview: Marie Whelan, CMA, is the Vice President of Finance & Administration, and Corporate Secretary, for lat49. Ms. Whelan has more than 15 years experience with public and private companies in the technology, biomedical, resource, and banking industries. In addition to her expertise in financial management, Ms. Whelan has a broad range of experience with issues in the area of financing, regulatory compliance, tax, corporate governance, and human resources.
